  "title": "Business Development Sales Executive | $3000 + Comms | Marymount - YZ11",
  "description": "<p><strong>Position Title: Sales Executive</strong></p>\n<p>Working location : Marymout</p>\n<p>Nearest MRT station: Marymount Station Exit B</p>\n<p>Working days : Mon to Fri</p>\n<p>Working hours : 9am - 5pm</p>\n<p>Salary: $3000 + Commission rate [To be discussed during interview]</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Reach out to new and potential customers in Singapore such as religious organisations, event organisers, live entertainment organisers and other businesses to generate sales to the company.</li>\n  <li>Attend to customers who walk into our stores.</li>\n  <li>Speak at ad-hoc product training workshops organised for end users.</li>\n  <li>Candidates take the initiative to strive for higher sales KPI.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum working experience of at least 2 years, preferably in the film/broadcast/lighting industries.</li>\n  <li>Has technical knowledge of cinematography, lighting, broadcast equipment and their applications</li>\n  <li>At least a diploma from a tertiary education institution</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid class 3 driving license.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Interested applicants, WA your resume to ‪‪‪‪+65 9136 9792‬‬‬‬ or email your resume to supreme.yentan@gmail.com.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>TAN YEN ZHEN (CHEN YANZHEN) REG NO: R25138932</p>\n<p>THE SUPREMEHR ADVISORY PTE LTD EA NO: 14C7279</p>",
